162
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,640
Bread!

163
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,680
Here, take it.

164
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,320
Take care.

165
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,280
Bread!

166
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,860
- Two for yourself?
- Bread, popsicles!

167
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:43,480
Bread and popsicles!

168
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,720
Come on, let's go in and play too.

169
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,680
Come play. It's on me.

170
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,240
What about ours?

171
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,440
What can you do?

172
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,400
- Good.
- I can do anything.

173
