178
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,920
You think I can't flatter Zhu Jiru?

179
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:20,280
I can't flatter Chu Jiahe?

180
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,760
You think I can't flatter people?

181
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,080
How could you do this?

182
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,520
Come back.

183
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,040
Get back here.

184
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:28,920
Come back.

185
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,680
For you

186
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,720
and the opera,

187
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:39,000
I spent my whole life savings.

188
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:42,040
And you hand out roles as favors?

189
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,360
Trading roles for favors, huh?

190
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,600
You'd better remember this.

191
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,000
Remember this.

192
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,480
Trading roles for favors, huh?

193
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,086
I'll make you remember.

194
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:50,120
Don't hit her like this.

195
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,080
- Get away.
- Stop.

196
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,360
You'll hurt her badly like this.

197
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,800
She should know opera comes
before everything.

198
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,000
It's no longer

199
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,600
the era of old opera troupes.

200
