You can't hit her as our master did.

201
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,440
If I don't hit her,

202
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:04,080
how will she learn my unique skills?

203
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:15,860
(Ningzhou County Qinqiang Opera Troupe)

204
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:20,420
See you on Monday.

205
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:21,760
- Okay.
- See you, Master Gou.

206
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,640
Okay.

207
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:33,880
Feng Xiaoxiao.

208
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,220
Who let you smoke?

209
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,560
Who let you smoke?

210
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,000
Who said you could smoke? Who?

211
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,200
Always talking nonsense.

212
00:12:39,370 --> 00:12:40,709
- Don't move.
- Talking nonsense.

213
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,960
- What's wrong?
- Don't move.

214
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:43,146
That's for talking nonsense.

215
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,480
I'll beat you senseless.

216
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:48,120
Talking nonsense.

217
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,600
Will you smoke again?

218
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,460
- Always talking nonsense.
- Smoking, huh?

219
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,835
- Back off.
- If you smoke again,

220
00:12:52,846 --> 00:12:53,840
I'll beat you.

221
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:54,760
You too.

222
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,340
- Behave yourselves.
- You two.

223
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,680
Behave yourselves.

224
00:12:57,680 --> 00:13:00,460
(Customer First)

225
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,760
Where did he hit you?

226
