229
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:12,200
Your head is bleeding.

230
00:13:14,887 --> 00:13:16,253
Come on, let's go to the hospital.

231
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,680
This is called breaking-out.

232
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:31,320
Breaking-out is
a Qinqiang opera skill.

233
00:13:31,866 --> 00:13:33,800
There's a full-length opera
called Li Hui Niang.

234
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:36,160
It's about a woman killed by a villain.

235
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,240
She returns as a ghost,

236
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:41,240
breathes fire, burns him down,

237
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:43,800
and saves the scholar she once loved.

238
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,000
Breaking-out is a rare skill,

239
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,880
especially the 81 Consecutive Bursts
of Fire.

240
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,960
Not everyone can pull it off.

241
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:55,480
At that final show of Gui Yuan Sha Sheng

242
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,800
in Beishan,

243
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:59,160
your master did
the 81 Consecutive Bursts of Fire,

244
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,800
but the last burst failed.

245
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,640
The show fell apart.

246
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:09,480
It haunted your master ever since.

247
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:14,600
We're going to the Beishan arts showcase

248
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,720
