249
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,480
One is your Yang Men Nyu Jiang.

250
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:22,320
The other is your master's
Gui Yuan Sha Sheng.

251
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:25,920
He wants that final burst of fire

252
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,240
to come out.

253
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,900
That's enough. Take a break.

254
00:14:40,906 --> 00:14:42,160
- I'm fine.
- Stop pushing it.

255
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,520
I'm fine. One more.

256
